'''托特里奇及惠特斯通站'''（{{lang-en|Totteridge & Whetstone tube station}}）是[[倫敦地鐵|倫敦地鐵]]的一個車站，位於[[北倫敦|北倫敦]][[巴尼特區|巴尼特區]][[惠特斯通|惠特斯通]]。托特里奇及惠特斯通站是[[北線|北線]]磨坊山支線的車站，位於倫敦第4收費區<ref>{{cite map/Standard Tube Map}}</ref>。車站位於托特里奇巷的北側<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com.my/maps/place/Totteridge+%26+Whetstone/@51.6302204,-0.1788689,17z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x487619da9d576bf9:0xd7ee8b78f8f8eff8 |title=Google Maps - Totteridge and Whetstone Tube Station |access-date=2016-03-01 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802140001/https://www.google.com.my/maps/place/Totteridge+%26+Whetstone/@51.6302204,-0.1788689,17z/data=%214m2%213m1%211s0x487619da9d576bf9:0xd7ee8b78f8f8eff8 }}</ref>，開通於1872年4月1日<ref name=CULG_1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.davros.org/rail/culg/northern.html#dates |title=Clive's Underground Line Guides - Northern Line, Dates |accessdate=2016-03-01 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929040829/http://www.davros.org/rail/culg/northern.html#dates |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
